The LLC Laptop Loan Policy at George Brown College has undergone changes as of December 18, 2023. The location for inquiries or applications is at Building B, 2nd Floor, Room 216, 300 Adelaide Street East, Toronto ON M5A 1N1. Contact information includes phone number 416-415-5000 ext. 6179 and TTY: 1-877-515-5559. The nearest subway station is King.

Additional contact details are 416-415-2000 and ask.george@georgebrown.ca. George Brown College's website contains information subject to change without notice, and it is the students' responsibility to verify fee requirements.
